title: The Difference Jesus Makes in Your Marriage
itunes:author: Guests: Ryan & Selena Frederick
itunes:summary: How can you and your spouse make it through the stormy seasons of life? As you'll learn from Greg, Erin and John, God's love can sustain your marriage no matter what you face. Receive the book Fierce Marriage with your gift of any amount!
